'''划界问题'''（{{lang-en|demarcation problem}}）是[[科学哲学|科学哲学]]中的重要问题，研究如何区分[[科学|科学]]与非科学（包括[[伪科学|伪科学]]、[[形而上学|形而上学]]以及[[文学|文学]]、[[艺术|艺术]]、[[信仰|信仰]]等其他非科学）的划界标准。<ref>{{cite journal |first=David B. |last=Resnik |doi=10.1016/S0039-3681(00)00004-2 |title=A pragmatic approach to the demarcation problem |journal=Studies In History and Philosophy of Science Part A |volume=31 |issue=2 |year=2000 |pages=249–267 }}</ref><ref name="Laudan1983">{{citation |last= Laudan |first= Larry |authorlink= Larry Laudan |editor1-last= Cohen |editor1-first= R.S. |editor2-last= Laudan |editor2-first= L. |title= Physics, Philosophy and Psychoanalysis: Essays in Honor of Adolf Grünbaum |series= Boston Studies in the Philosophy of Science |volume= 76 |year= 1983 |publisher= D. Reidel |location= Dordrecht |isbn= 90-277-1533-5 |pages= 111–127 |chapter= The Demise of the Demarcation Problem |url= https://books.google.com/books?id=AEvprSJzv2MC&pg=PA111 |accessdate= 2016-12-04 |archive-date= 2020-08-02 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200802035350/https://books.google.com/books?id=AEvprSJzv2MC&pg=PA111 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name="Lakatos1999">{{cite book |first=I. |last=Lakatos |first2=P. |last2=Feyerabend |first3=M. |last3=Motterlini |year=1999 |title=For and Against Method: Including Lakatos's Lectures on Scientific Method and the Lakatos-Feyerabend Correspondence |publisher=University of Chicago Press |isbn=9780226467740 |lccn=99013581 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=osMnuvLZvPoC&pg=PA20 |page=20 |access-date=2016-12-04 |archive-date=2020-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200715204704/https://books.google.com/books?id=osMnuvLZvPoC&pg=PA20 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title=《哲学大辞典·上》|editor=冯契|year=2007|publisher=上海辞书出版社}}</ref>[[卡尔·波普尔|卡尔·波普尔]]称其为科学哲学的核心问题。

20世纪初[[逻辑实证主义|逻辑实证主义]]者发展出的{{le|证实主义|verificationism}}理论认为可证实性是区分科学与形而上学的标准。他们认为一个陈述只有在经验中得到证实，才是有意义的、是科学的。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=kYUFhlIRZA4C&pg=PT97&dq=demarcation+%22logical+positivism%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=Z9n8U7vdEuKw7AbYgIG4DA&ved=0CDoQ6AEwBDhG#v=onepage&q=demarcation%20%22logical%20positivism%22&f=false |title=Grayling, AC., ''Wittgenstein: A Very Short Introduction'', Oxford University Press, 2001, pp. 67-68. |accessdate=2016-12-04 |archive-date=2020-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200220153426/https://books.google.com/books?id=kYUFhlIRZA4C&pg=PT97&dq=demarcation+%22logical+positivism%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=Z9n8U7vdEuKw7AbYgIG4DA&ved=0CDoQ6AEwBDhG#v=onepage&q=demarcation%20%22logical%20positivism%22&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[卡尔·波普尔|卡尔·波普尔]]则提出了与可证实性相对的[[可证伪性|可证伪性]]，认为是否可被经验证伪才是判断科学与否的标准。<ref name="sep-pseudo-science">{{cite web |first=Sven Ove |last=Hansson |editor-first=Edward N. |editor-last=Zalta |year=2008 |title=Science and Pseudo-Science |work=The Stanford Encyclopedia of Philosophy |edition=Fall 2008 |url=http://plato.stanford.edu/archives/fall2008/entries/pseudo-science#KarPop |at=4.2 Falsificationism |accessdate=2016-12-04 |archive-date=2019-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190318123600/https://plato.stanford.edu/archives/fall2008/entries/pseudo-science/#KarPop |dead-url=no }}</ref>此外，他认为这是一个划界标准，而非逻辑实证主义中的意义标准。

此后，[[托马斯·库恩|托马斯·库恩]]在其代表作《[[科学革命的结构|科学革命的结构]]》中提出的[[范式转移|范式转移]]理论，则将科学发展分为{{le|常规科学|normal science}}与非常规科学。他指出在常规科学时期科学共同体在已有的一套范式中从事解难题活动，是区分科学与其他领域的标准。<ref name="sep-pseudo-science"/>[[伊姆雷·拉卡托斯|伊姆雷·拉卡托斯]]则批判地继承了被其称为“朴素证伪主义”的波普尔思想，同时借鉴了库恩范式理论，从而发展出了精致证伪主义的[[研究纲领|研究纲领]]方法论，提出将研究纲领是进步的还是退步的作为划界标准。与逻辑实证主义与波普尔证伪主义不同，库恩与拉卡托斯的科学划界标准都是历史的与相对的。

[[保罗·费耶阿本德|保罗·费耶阿本德]]、{{le|拉里·劳丹|Larry Laudan}}等科学哲学家则主张消解划界问题。费耶阿本德就认为不应该划分科学与非科学<ref name="Taylor1996">{{cite book |first=C.A. |last=Taylor |year=1996 |title=Defining Science: A Rhetoric of Demarcation |series=Rhetoric of the Human Sciences Series |publisher=University of Wisconsin Press |isbn=9780299150341 |lccn=96000180 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=NdkDiqh5ySYC&pg=PA41 |page=41 |access-date=2016-12-04 |archive-date=2019-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609230416/https://books.google.com/books?id=NdkDiqh5ySYC&pg=PA41 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，劳丹则认为划分问题是个虚假的问题，这样的标准是无法找到的。<ref name="Laudan1983"/>

除此之外，[[保罗·萨伽德|保罗·萨伽德]]、{{le|马里奥·邦格|Mario Bunge}}等则分别提出了多元的划界标准。与科学哲学传统中单一的划界标准不同，他们各自都给出了一组若干条评判标准来区别科学与非科学。<ref>[http://www.cavehill.uwi.edu/bnccde/PH29A/thagard.html ''Why Astrology Is A Pseudoscience''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cavehill.uwi.edu/bnccde/PH29A/thagard.html |date=20081201161104 }}, Paul R. Thagard, In Philosophy of Science Association 1978 Volume 1, edited by P.D. Asquith and I. Hacking (East Lansing: Philosophy of Science Association, 1978).</ref><ref>{{cite journal|title=科学划界的多元标准|author=陈健|journal=自然辩证法通讯|year=1996|issue=3|url=http://www.cssn.cn/zhx/zx_kxjszx/201604/t20160420_2976548.shtml|access-date=2016-12-04|archive-date=2016-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161223012901/http://www.cssn.cn/zhx/zx_kxjszx/201604/t20160420_2976548.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

